WEBVTT

00:05.170 --> 00:10.005
Captions made possible by
HOME BOX OFFICE, INC.

01:43.500 --> 01:44.660
HELLO !

01:48.070 --> 01:49.935
HELLO !

01:50.040 --> 01:51.564
DAMN IT.

01:51.670 --> 01:53.831
IF IT HASN'T WORKED
FOR THE LAST 45 MINUTES,

01:53.940 --> 01:55.305
IT'S NOT
GONNA WORK NOW.

01:55.410 --> 01:58.174
THAT GODDAMN NIGHT GUARD
MUST BE DRUNK AND DEAF.

01:58.280 --> 02:00.510
I'LL TRY
MY PHONE AGAIN.

02:00.620 --> 02:02.076
WE'VE ALREADY
TRIED OUR PHONES.

02:02.190 --> 02:03.282
WE DON'T GET RECEPTION
UP HERE, ALRIGHT ?

02:03.390 --> 02:05.381
JUST WAIT FOR
THE RESCUE TEAMS.

02:10.960 --> 02:12.086
SHIT.

02:12.200 --> 02:13.326
SHIT.

02:13.430 --> 02:15.990
DON'T DO THAT,
YOU COULD MAKE IT WORSE !

02:16.100 --> 02:17.465
WE HAVE
TO DO SOMETHING.

02:17.570 --> 02:19.060
OKAY, LET'S ALL TRY TO PRY
THIS DOOR OPEN ONE MORE TIME.

02:19.170 --> 02:21.138
GIVE IT
EVERYTHING WE GOT.

02:24.510 --> 02:26.831
WERE GONNA DROP 10 FLOORS,
AND WE'RE ALL GONNA DIE !

02:26.940 --> 02:30.546
WE COULD USE A LITTLE MORE
BRUCE WILLIS A'I'I'ITUDE, MISTER.

02:38.190 --> 02:41.455
LEMME OUT, LEMME OUT !

02:41.560 --> 02:43.084
NO WAY, YOU'RE BEING
SO OBNOXIOUS.

02:43.190 --> 02:46.421
GET UP THERE,
WE'LL GIVE YOU A BOOST.

02:50.230 --> 02:51.891
I'LL TAKE THE STAIRS,
I'LL GET SOME HELP--

02:52.000 --> 02:53.297
GOD, WE'RE ALL
GONNA DIE--

02:53.400 --> 02:56.267
STOP IT, STOP IT,
STOP IT !

02:56.370 --> 02:57.507
SOMEBODY GRAB
MY HAND.

02:57.610 --> 02:59.373
NO, SHE
SHOULD GO FIRST !

02:59.480 --> 03:01.368
GO.

03:02.280 --> 03:03.144
OH, MY GOD.

03:03.250 --> 03:04.547
KEN, GET IN HERE.

03:04.650 --> 03:05.708
NO, NO, NO !

03:05.810 --> 03:07.072
OH, MY GOD !

03:07.180 --> 03:12.015
AAHH, NO !

03:12.120 --> 03:14.213
( screaming )

03:40.250 --> 03:42.844
( explosion )
( glass breaking )

03:44.290 --> 03:45.086
OH, MY GOD !

03:45.190 --> 03:46.088
WHAT HAPPENED ?!

03:46.190 --> 03:47.657
GO FIND OUT
WHAT HAPPENED !

03:47.760 --> 03:48.988
LET'S BOTH GO.

03:49.090 --> 03:50.182
I THINK WE SHOULD
STAY TOGETHER.

03:50.290 --> 03:51.757
I'M TOO SCARED.

03:55.600 --> 03:57.898
GEORGE, THE GLASS
PUT ON YOUR SLIPPERS.

04:08.040 --> 04:09.598
( sirens )

04:34.640 --> 04:35.891
GEORGE.

04:41.840 --> 04:43.808
WHAT DID YOU DO ?

04:46.110 --> 04:47.543
GEORGE ?

04:53.020 --> 04:55.181
GEORGE ?

04:55.290 --> 04:56.518
GEORGE ?

04:56.630 --> 04:58.029
GEORGE ?

04:59.290 --> 05:00.723
I'M AWAKE.

05:00.830 --> 05:04.596
YOU WERE WHIMPERING
AND PADDLING WITH YOUR FEET.

05:04.700 --> 05:06.668
WHAT WERE YOU
DREAMING ABOUT ?

05:09.100 --> 05:10.601
I DON'T REMEMBER.

05:23.990 --> 05:27.653
( alarm clock)

05:32.460 --> 05:34.519
YEAH, IT'S AT THE BELLANDI
GALLERY DOWNTOWN,

05:34.630 --> 05:37.428
WHERE JIMMY WAS,
YOU GOT MY POSTCARD, RIGHT ?

05:37.530 --> 05:39.464
OKAY, WELL CALL ME
IF YOU DO NEED DIRECTIONS.

05:39.570 --> 05:42.038
ALRIGHT, I'LL
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

05:42.140 --> 05:44.438
OH, BRING COOL PEOPLE.

05:50.280 --> 05:52.771
OH HI, EDIE,
IT'S CLAIRE.

05:54.520 --> 05:55.817
LISTEN, TOMORROW
IS MY SHOW.

05:55.920 --> 05:58.286
I KNOW YOU PROBABLY
WON'T BE THERE BUT--

05:58.390 --> 06:02.349
I WISH YOU
WOULD BE THERE.

06:04.290 --> 06:05.928
OKAY, SHIT,
NEVER MIND.

06:15.540 --> 06:16.962
I BROKE UP
WITH RUSSELL.

06:17.070 --> 06:18.162
WHY ?

06:18.270 --> 06:19.635
WHY DO
YOU THINK ?

06:19.740 --> 06:22.379
HE'S A BIG DRAMA QUEEN,
EVERYTHING'S SO HEAW

06:22.480 --> 06:24.243
AND NEGATIVE, HE'S
SUCH A FUCKING VICTIM.

06:24.350 --> 06:26.648
YEAH, REALLY.

06:26.750 --> 06:29.548
HE GOT IN MY FACE
ABOUT YOUR SHOW.

06:29.650 --> 06:32.483
OH, GOD,
HE'S UNBELIEVABLE.

06:32.590 --> 06:35.559
I WAS LIKE,
"WHOEVER'S IDEA IT WAS

06:35.660 --> 06:37.685
AND I DON'T FUCKING CARE,
CLAIRE RAN WITH IT".

06:37.790 --> 06:40.054
I WAS LIKE,
"ADAPT, DUDE".

06:41.860 --> 06:43.896
THANK YOU
FOR DEFENDING MY HONOR.

06:45.870 --> 06:48.259
HEY, I BROUGHT YOU
A PRESENT.

06:48.370 --> 06:50.565
HAPPY FAME.

06:52.270 --> 06:54.807
OH, MY GOD,
IS THAT COCAINE ?

06:54.910 --> 06:57.276
THIS IS SO DISCO !

06:57.380 --> 06:58.745
LET'S DO
A FEW LINES.

06:58.850 --> 07:01.375
OH SHIT, I WANT TO BUT
I HAVE TO GO TO MY GALLERY

07:01.480 --> 07:03.345
AND MEET SOME
HUGE MOVIE STAR.

07:03.450 --> 07:05.111
SERIOUSLY ?

07:05.220 --> 07:06.517
WHAT MOVIE STAR ?

07:06.620 --> 07:08.315
I DON'T KNOW,
SOME LIKE CELEBRITY WOMAN

07:08.420 --> 07:10.149
WANTS TO BUY
MY STUFF.

07:10.260 --> 07:12.285
YOU'RE GETTING
WAY TOO COOL FOR ME.

07:12.390 --> 07:14.449
FUCK YOU.

07:14.560 --> 07:17.893
NO, IT'S
A FISH TAIL.

07:18.000 --> 07:20.036
IT'S A FISH TAIL !

07:20.140 --> 07:21.289
YES.

07:21.400 --> 07:23.209
I'M CALLING
THE LAWYER AGAIN.

07:23.310 --> 07:24.504
WHERE'S THE PHONE ?

07:24.610 --> 07:25.861
YOU'RE TOO CLEVER,
HE ALREADY TOLD YOU.

07:25.970 --> 07:27.403
YEAH, I KNOW
HE ALREADY SAID THAT

07:27.510 --> 07:29.478
BARB HAS NO
RIGHT TO CUSTODY,

07:29.580 --> 07:31.241
BUT I JUST SAW THIS
ARTICLE ON THE NET--

07:31.350 --> 07:33.443
YOU'RE THE FATHER,
BARB'S THE AUNT,

07:33.550 --> 07:34.812
MAYA'S STAYING
RIGHT HERE WHERE SHE IS.

07:34.920 --> 07:37.980
YOU'RE NOT TAKING
THIS SERIOUSLY.

07:38.090 --> 07:40.308
YES, I AM, BUT IT DOESN'T
DO US ANY GOOD TO LIVE

07:40.420 --> 07:41.887
IN THIS CONSTANT
STATE OF PANIC.

07:41.990 --> 07:43.855
WELL, THAT'S EASY FOR YOU
TO SAY, MAYA'S NOT YOURS.

07:43.960 --> 07:46.224
YES, CAN YOU REACH
MR. SUTCLIFFE FOR ME, PLEASE.

07:46.330 --> 07:48.127
NATE FISHER.

07:48.230 --> 07:49.595
IT'S AN EMERGENCY.

07:49.700 --> 07:51.668
THIS ISN'T ABOUT MAYA,
IT'S ABOUT YOUR EMOTIONS

07:51.770 --> 07:53.260
AND HOW YOU
DEAL WITH THEM.

07:53.370 --> 07:54.394
WILL YOU STOP USING
THE THERAPY VOICE,

07:55.640 --> 07:57.335
HOW WOULD YOU KNOW ?

07:57.440 --> 07:58.236
YOU'VE NEVER
TRIED THERAPY.

07:58.340 --> 07:59.432
I DON'T
NEED THERAPY.

07:59.540 --> 08:01.132
IT'S NOT MY FAULT
THERE'S A DISASTER

08:01.240 --> 08:02.332
EVERY TIME
I BLINK.

08:02.440 --> 08:03.247
WHAT'S WITH
THIS BOOK ?

08:03.350 --> 08:04.499
IT'S MACABRE.

08:04.610 --> 08:05.702
LET'S GET RID OF IT
OR PUT IT AWAY.

08:05.810 --> 08:07.141
MICHAELA GAVE IT TO ME
TO GIVE TO DAVID.

08:07.250 --> 08:08.512
I KEEP FORGE'ITING
ABOUT IT.

08:08.620 --> 08:10.508
I REALLY WISH
YOU'D CONSIDER IT--

08:10.620 --> 08:12.019
LOOK, EVERYTHING
IS UNDER CONTROL !

08:12.120 --> 08:15.089
OF COURSE IT IS.

08:24.200 --> 08:25.497
NUMBER THREE.

08:25.600 --> 08:27.261
EXCUSE ME ?

08:27.370 --> 08:30.009
THAT'S HIM,
NUMBER THREE.

08:34.310 --> 08:35.402
DAVID.

08:35.510 --> 08:37.148
DAVID,
IT'S ALMOST 11.

08:37.250 --> 08:38.000
ARE YOU GOING
TO GET UP ?

08:38.110 --> 08:39.816
YEAH.

08:43.090 --> 08:44.614
WHAT ?

08:44.720 --> 08:48.588
I'M STILL REPLAYING
THAT FUCKING LOOK HE GAVE ME.

08:49.830 --> 08:51.252
DO YOU WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT ?

08:51.360 --> 08:53.555
NO, I DON'T WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT.

08:53.660 --> 08:56.561
I'VE TOLD YOU
ABOUT IT 900 TIMES,

08:56.670 --> 08:59.127
I'VE TOLD MY THERAPIST
ABOUT IT 900 TIMES,

08:59.230 --> 09:01.369
I WANT TO FUCKING MOVE ON
AND LEAVE IT BEHIND ME.

09:01.470 --> 09:03.028
SO DO IT.

09:04.070 --> 09:05.002
YOU CAN.

09:05.110 --> 09:06.031
NO, I CAN'T.

09:06.140 --> 09:08.870
I'M FUCKING STUCK.

09:08.980 --> 09:12.279
IF YOU COULD DO ANYTHING,
WHAT WOULD YOU DO ?

09:14.080 --> 09:18.119
I'D TELL HIM WHAT I THINK
OF HIM AND WHAT HE DID TO ME,

09:18.220 --> 09:19.778
THAT EVIL, EVIL FUCK.

09:19.890 --> 09:21.118
WELL, YOU CAN
DO THAT.

09:21.220 --> 09:24.929
I KNOW, I SAID IT ALL
TO THE THERAPY PILLOW.

09:25.030 --> 09:27.555
NO, YOU CAN
VISIT HIM IN JAIL.

09:29.430 --> 09:30.727
WHAT ?!

09:30.830 --> 09:33.492
MAYBE HE'LL SEE YOU, MAYBE
HE WON'T, BUT YOU CAN TRY.

09:33.600 --> 09:35.158
ARE YOU SERIOUS ?

09:35.270 --> 09:36.601
YES, I AM.

09:36.710 --> 09:38.860
I THINK IT WOULD
BE EXTREMELY SELF-DESTRUCT IVE

09:38.970 --> 09:40.699
TO PUT MYSELF
IN THAT SITUATION !

09:40.810 --> 09:43.347
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU'D
EVEN SUGGEST IT TO ME.

09:53.220 --> 09:54.778
TWO HOURS, GREAT !

09:54.890 --> 09:57.427
LET ME KNOW WHEN YOU'RE ON THE
GROUND AND I'LL COME MEET YOU.

09:57.530 --> 09:59.589
ME, TOO.

09:59.700 --> 10:02.760
BYE-BYE.

10:09.870 --> 10:12.361
MY DAUGHTER'S ON HER WAY
TO HAWAII FOR A CONFERENCE

10:12.470 --> 10:14.734
AND SHE HAS A LAYOVER
THIS AFTERNOON.

10:14.840 --> 10:18.446
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO MEET HER FOR LUNCH ?

10:18.550 --> 10:20.108
MAGGIE ?

10:20.220 --> 10:21.278
REALLY ?

10:21.380 --> 10:23.109
OH, YES !

10:23.220 --> 10:25.984
THIS IS SO
EXCITING !

10:26.090 --> 10:28.479
WHAT KIND
OF CONFERENCE ?

10:28.590 --> 10:30.057
I DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT HER.

10:30.160 --> 10:31.184
WHAT DOES SHE DO ?

10:31.290 --> 10:32.382
PHARMACEUTICAL REP.

10:32.490 --> 10:33.855
YOU'RE PROUD OF HER,
I CAN TELL.

10:33.960 --> 10:36.724
SHE'S THE APPLE
OF YOUR EYE.

10:38.300 --> 10:40.097
I KNOW YOU'RE DOING
THIS FOR ME, TOO, GEORGE.

10:40.200 --> 10:41.667
THANK YOU.

10:41.770 --> 10:43.169
YOU'LL LIKE HER.

10:43.270 --> 10:45.761
I CAN'T WAIT !

10:49.140 --> 10:51.540
I'M NOT THE PERSON
WHO'S SUPPOSED TO BE HERE,

10:51.650 --> 10:53.914
WE'VE BEEN DIVORCED
FOR AGES.

10:54.020 --> 10:57.979
HE MUST HAVE A NEW WIFE
OR A GIRLFRIEND.

11:00.990 --> 11:02.821
YOU WERE HIS
EMERGENCY CONTACT.

11:02.930 --> 11:05.057
HE WORKED AT THE SAME
PLACE FOR 25 YEARS,

11:05.160 --> 11:07.390
I'M SURE HE JUST FORGOT
TO CHANGE THE FORM.

11:10.500 --> 11:12.024
MAYBE HE STILL
LOVED YOU.

11:14.840 --> 11:16.364
HE'S A VERY
NICE GUY,

11:16.470 --> 11:18.267
BUT YOU KNOW...

11:18.370 --> 11:20.770
I'VE MOVED ON.

11:20.880 --> 11:23.201
WELL, I'M SORRY,
BUT THERE ARE DECISIONS

11:23.310 --> 11:24.709
ABOUT THE FUNERAL
THAT HAVE TO BE MADE.

11:24.810 --> 11:26.277
YES, WELL, I DON'T
WANT TO MAKE THEM !

11:26.380 --> 11:29.747
NOW THERE MUST BE SOMEONE
ELSE WHO CAN DEAL WITH THIS.

11:29.850 --> 11:31.147
'CAUSE I CAN'T
BELIEVE IT !

11:31.250 --> 11:33.650
HOW CAN YOU GET KILLED
BY AN ELEVATOR ?

11:33.760 --> 11:36.149
WELL, THERE WERE THREE
OTHER PEOPLE TRAPPED INSIDE.

11:36.260 --> 11:38.956
AND HE TRIED TO GET THEM OUT AND
THE ELEVATOR TORE HIM IN HALF.

11:40.500 --> 11:42.058
(vomiting )

11:50.440 --> 11:51.634
I HIT A NEW LOW.

11:51.740 --> 11:55.176
I MADE
THE BEREAVED VOMIT.

11:56.610 --> 11:58.373
DON'T TELL ME WE HAVE TO SEND
THIS GUY SOMEWHERE ELSE,

11:58.480 --> 11:59.344
I JUST
EMBALMED HIM.

11:59.450 --> 12:03.147
NO, NO, WE
WORKED IT OUT.

12:03.250 --> 12:05.844
I THINK IT'S WEIRD
WE DON'T SEW HIM TOGETHER.

12:08.060 --> 12:10.153
ONCE HE'S IN THE CASKET,
DRESSED, WITH A LITTLE PADDING,

12:10.260 --> 12:11.454
CAN'T EVEN TELL
THE DIFFERENCE.

12:11.560 --> 12:14.495
HERE, IT'S A PRESENT
FROM MICHAELA.

12:16.330 --> 12:18.594
WHAT A SWEET KID.

12:18.700 --> 12:21.396
LITTLE MORBID,
BUT SWEET.

12:23.270 --> 12:26.307
SO UNLIKE HER MOTHER,
THAT CRAZY BITCH FROM HELL.

12:27.480 --> 12:29.129
WHAT'S THAT ?

12:39.190 --> 12:41.909
( male )
It's Roger Pasquese,
does that ring a bell ?

12:42.790 --> 12:43.722
YEAH.

12:43.830 --> 12:45.855
YEAH, IT DOES.

12:46.630 --> 12:47.995
HOW ARE YOU,
KEITH ?

12:48.100 --> 12:50.261
I'M FINE,
A LITTLE SURPRISED.

12:50.370 --> 12:51.860
HOW ARE YOU ?

12:51.970 --> 12:53.039
I'm well,
thank you.

12:53.140 --> 12:55.461
ENJOYING THE DAY,
CARPE DIEM.

12:55.570 --> 12:57.060
YEAH, THAT'S GREAT.

12:57.170 --> 12:58.137
WHAT'S UP ?

12:58.240 --> 13:01.573
I'm taking a break
from angry ugly white men.

13:01.680 --> 13:03.341
LET'S TAKE IT
EASY NOW, HUH ?

13:03.450 --> 13:06.601
Okay, seriously.

13:06.710 --> 13:08.018
I HAVE A BUSINESS
PROPOSITION FOR YOU

13:08.120 --> 13:10.247
AND I'D LIKE
FOR US TO MEET.

13:10.350 --> 13:11.282
WHAT DO YOU SAY,

13:11.390 --> 13:12.311
YOU COME TO
MY HOUSE AND WE TALK ?

13:12.420 --> 13:13.887
PROBABLY NOT.

13:13.990 --> 13:15.150
NOTHING AGAINST YOU.

13:15.260 --> 13:16.511
IT JUST DOESN'T SEEM LIKE
A VERY GOOD IDEA.

13:16.620 --> 13:18.759
But thanks, anyway.

13:18.860 --> 13:21.920
YOU KNOW, CERTAIN PAPERS
HAVE YET TO BE SIGNED.

13:22.030 --> 13:26.126
Our lawsuit might
rear its ugly head again.

13:27.270 --> 13:29.397
ROGER, WE HAD
AN AGREEMENT.

13:29.500 --> 13:32.799
I DON'T THINK A BLOWJOB
IS LEGAL OR BINDING.

13:32.910 --> 13:34.468
How about
tomorrow afternoon ?

13:34.580 --> 13:35.808
I'LL THINK
ABOUT IT.

13:35.910 --> 13:39.073
WELL, YOU SEE NICOLE,
CLAIRE HAS A PLURALITY

13:39.180 --> 13:42.308
OF INFLUENCES
AT WORK HERE.

13:42.420 --> 13:45.116
THEY'RE PORTRAITS,
AN ANCIENT, CLASSICAL FORM,

13:45.220 --> 13:47.586
AND THEY'RE PHOTOGRAPHS,
WHICH ARE ESSENTIALLY MODERN.

13:47.690 --> 13:49.351
AND THEN THEY'RE
TORN TO BITS.

13:49.460 --> 13:52.588
A NOD TO THE DADAISTS,
AND THE CUBISTS AS WELL.

13:52.690 --> 13:54.897
THEN THE PIECES
ARE REASSEMBLED

13:55.000 --> 13:58.891
FOR A DECONSTRUCTED MIX
OF DETACHMENT AND TENDERNESS

13:59.000 --> 14:03.004
WHICH SEEMS TO ME TO BE
VERY NEW MILLENNIUM.

14:04.140 --> 14:06.608
ANYTHING YOU'D
LIKE TO ADD, CLAIRE ?

14:08.440 --> 14:10.579
UM, WELL...

14:12.310 --> 14:14.915
WHAT YOU SAID
IS PART OF IT.

14:16.550 --> 14:18.518
OF COURSE, IT'S MORE
INVOLVED THAN THAT--

14:18.620 --> 14:20.952
I TOTALLY GET IT.

14:21.060 --> 14:26.657
IT REMINDS ME OF PAPER DOLLS
AND BAD RELATIONSHIPS

14:26.760 --> 14:29.422
AND LIES PEOPLE TELL
ABOUT STUPID THINGS.

14:29.530 --> 14:31.327
RIGHT ?

14:31.430 --> 14:32.590
RIGHT.

14:32.700 --> 14:34.964
IS THIS ALL
YOU HAVE ?

14:35.070 --> 14:37.061
AS A MATTER OF FACT,

14:37.170 --> 14:39.866
SHE'S WORKING HARD
ON A WHOLE NEW SERIES.

14:39.980 --> 14:41.572
IT LOOKS
VERY PROMISING.

14:41.680 --> 14:43.545
COOL, WHEN
CAN I SEE IT ?

14:45.910 --> 14:46.706
SOON.

14:46.810 --> 14:47.913
VERY SOON.

14:48.020 --> 14:50.079
I HAVE TO FIGURE
OUT SOME STUFF.

14:51.320 --> 14:54.312
WE USED TO COME TO
THIS PLACE WHEN I WAS A GIRL.

14:54.420 --> 14:57.628
SARAH AND I WOULD EAT THOUSAND
ISLAND DRESSING ALL BY ITSELF.

14:58.760 --> 15:00.296
WHAT A TREAT !

15:00.400 --> 15:01.856
I LIKE THIS PLACE.

15:01.960 --> 15:04.497
THE MENU
NEVER CHANGES

15:04.600 --> 15:07.433
AND THIS BUILDING HAS STOOD
THROUGH ALL THE MUDSLIDES,

15:07.540 --> 15:09.064
FIRES, EARTHQUAKES.

15:09.170 --> 15:11.206
YES,
IT'S COM FORTING.

15:13.480 --> 15:14.299
MAGGIE !

15:14.410 --> 15:15.900
DADDY !

15:19.810 --> 15:20.845
HI!

15:20.950 --> 15:24.010
OH, SWEETIE, IT'S
GREAT TO SEE YOU.

15:24.120 --> 15:26.987
THIS IS WONDERFUL.

15:34.130 --> 15:36.223
WITH MANAGED CARE
THE WAY THAT IT IS,

15:36.330 --> 15:39.060
MOST OF THESE SAMPLES THAT
I HAUL AROUND END UP

15:39.170 --> 15:42.094
GOING TO PATIENTS WHO CAN'T
AFFORD TO PAY FOR PRESCRIPTIONS,

15:42.200 --> 15:46.068
SO EVERYBODY AT THE DOCTOR'S
OFFICE IS GLAD TO SEE MAGGIE.

15:48.280 --> 15:50.475
SO, WHAT'S NEW
IN ANTIBIOTICS ?

15:54.820 --> 15:56.981
A COURSE OF THIS WILL
KNOCK OUT JUST ABOUT ANYTHING.

15:57.090 --> 15:58.182
BUT YOU HAVE TO TAKE
THE WHOLE SEVEN DAYS.

15:58.290 --> 16:00.281
HUH, ANY SIDE EFFECTS ?

16:00.390 --> 16:03.382
MINIMAL, MAYBE A LITTLE NAUSEA,
SO TAKE IT WITH FOOD.

16:03.490 --> 16:05.287
THANKS, HON.

16:05.390 --> 16:06.948
ARE YOU SICK ?

16:07.630 --> 16:09.894
NO.

16:10.000 --> 16:12.195
I JUST WANT
TO BE PREPARED.

16:12.300 --> 16:15.633
OF COURSE THESE THINGS
WON'T TOUCH ANYTHING VIRAL.

16:15.740 --> 16:18.436
DID YOU KNOW THAT YOU
CAN ORDER POTASSIUM IODIDE

16:18.540 --> 16:19.962
OFF THE INTERNET NOW ?

16:20.080 --> 16:21.308
OH, THAT'S GREAT.

16:21.410 --> 16:23.970
THAT IS SO MUCH
MORE CONVENIENT.

16:26.110 --> 16:28.374
WHAT'S POTASSIUM
IODIDE ?

16:28.480 --> 16:30.584
ANTI-RADIATION.

16:30.690 --> 16:33.011
IF YOU TAKE IT IN TIME,
IT BLOCKS THE THYROID'S UPTAKE

16:33.120 --> 16:37.250
OF AIRBORNE RADIOACTIVE IODINE
FROM A NUCLEAR ACCIDENT.

16:37.360 --> 16:39.248
LET'S NOT WORRY
TODAY, DAD.

16:40.060 --> 16:41.652
WE'RE OKAY TODAY.

16:42.960 --> 16:45.064
OF COURSE WE ARE.

16:52.270 --> 16:55.034
OKAY, I'D LIKE TO TALK
ABOUT THIS MORNING.

