I'M ALL BUZZY.

21:39.130 --> 21:40.529
DID YOU GET INTO
THAT BLOW WITHOUT ME ?

21:40.630 --> 21:43.565
NO, LOOK, IT'S MY
FIRST EXHIBITION,

21:43.670 --> 21:44.967
THERE'S ALL
THIS STRESS.

21:45.070 --> 21:46.799
CLAIRE.

21:46.900 --> 21:48.333
ONE NIGHT.

21:48.440 --> 21:50.601
