NEVER MADE IT TO SANTA CRUZ ?

23:02.180 --> 23:03.408
I DON'T KNOW.

23:03.510 --> 23:04.602
THERE'S PROBABLY
A SIMPLE EXPLANATION.

23:04.710 --> 23:05.972
THEN I WANT
TO FUCKING HEAR IT.

23:06.080 --> 23:07.104
I'M GOING UP THERE.

23:07.210 --> 23:08.609
OH, GOD, THIS IS NEVER
GOING TO END.

23:10.620 --> 23:11.882
DON'T YOU FUCKING REALIZE
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE ?

23:11.990 --> 23:13.218
THERE WAS SOMEBODY
THERE WITH HER.

23:13.320 --> 23:14.287
SOMEBODY TOOK
THIS PICTURE.

23:14.390 --> 23:15.709
OKAY, LOOK.

23:15.820 --> 23:17.856
