MY IMAGINATION ?

24:27.760 --> 24:29.398
NO.

24:29.500 --> 24:32.594
THE AIR IS POISONED,
GEORGE.

24:32.700 --> 24:35.760
IT'S A SCIENTIFIC FACT.

24:35.870 --> 24:37.599
THEY TOOK BLOOD SAMPLES
FROM A REMOTE VILLAGE

24:37.710 --> 24:41.430
OF INDIANS
IN BOLIVIA.

24:41.540 --> 24:44.202
ALTO LOS ZARZOS.

24:44.310 --> 24:45.846
EVEN THEY WERE
CONTAMINATED.

24:45.950 --> 24:48.510
THERE ARE CHEMICALS
IN THE RAIN.

24:50.320 --> 24:52.743
