HAPPENING.

24:55.620 --> 24:58.953
YES, I KNOW, BUT--

24:59.060 --> 24:59.879
OUR DAYS ARE NUMBERED.

24:59.990 --> 25:02.220
IT'S ONLY
A MATTER OF TIME.

25:02.330 --> 25:06.118
BUT I TRULY BELIEVE
IF WE PREPARE--

25:06.230 --> 25:07.697
DON'T BE NAIVE,
GEORGE.

25:07.800 --> 25:09.131
YOU WEREN'T
BROUGHT UP THAT WAY.

25:09.240 --> 25:11.538
THERE'S NO HOPE.

25:11.640 --> 25:14.370
