I CAN'T GIVE UP.

25:22.520 --> 25:23.782
NO.

25:24.620 --> 25:26.178
NO, I WON'T.

25:48.180 --> 25:49.101
ARE YOU ALRIGHT ?

25:49.210 --> 25:50.029
YES.

25:50.140 --> 25:52.779
NO.

25:53.950 --> 25:56.271
COULD YOU...

25:56.380 --> 25:58.086
