SIT WITH ME ?

26:00.190 --> 26:01.179
OKAY.

26:09.330 --> 26:10.456
THE WAY HE DIED,
OH GOD.

26:10.560 --> 26:12.892
GOD, IT'S AWFUL.

26:13.000 --> 26:15.730
I CAN'T STOP
THINKING ABOUT IT.

26:15.840 --> 26:19.435
IF THERE WAS ANYONE WHO
DESERVED TO GO IN THEIR SLEEP,

26:19.540 --> 26:22.179
IT WAS KEN.

26:23.710 --> 26:27.498
IT'S THE WAY THAT KEN
LIVED THAT'S IMPORTANT.

26:27.620 --> 26:29.144
WE WEREN'T CLOSE
ANYMORE.

26:32.890 --> 26:34.619
HE WAS YOUR
HUSBAND ONCE.

26:34.720 --> 26:36.688
15 YEARS AGO.

26:36.790 --> 26:40.578
HONESTLY, WHEN I GOT
THE CALL, I HAD TO THINK,

26:40.700 --> 26:43.123
"KEN, KEN WHO" ?

26:46.000 --> 26:50.562
THEN I REMEMBERED,
EVERY MINUTE WE SPENT TOGETHER,

26:50.670 --> 26:53.161
I REMEMBER EVERYTHING.

26:55.210 --> 26:58.805
I'M GOING TO BURY HIM
WITH THE REST OF MY FAMILY.

27:00.920 --> 27:02.945
THAT'S THE WAY IT SHOULD BE,
DON'T YOU THINK ?

27:03.050 --> 27:06.383
YES, YES, I DO.

27:06.490 --> 27:07.980
EVEN IF
I MARRY AGAIN...

27:08.090 --> 27:12.823
WHEN I'M DEAD
I WANT KEN THERE, TOO.

27:13.660 --> 27:14.592
FAMILY'S FAMILY.

27:14.700 --> 27:16.429
DIVORCE DOESN'T
CHANGE THAT.

27:16.530 --> 27:20.364
NOT DIVORCE, NOT DEATH,
NOT ANYTHING.

27:20.470 --> 27:23.564
WHEN PEOPLE...

27:23.670 --> 27:26.332
GET IN YOUR HEART ?

27:26.440 --> 27:28.237
