FOR GOOD.

27:40.960 --> 27:42.188
MAGGIE,
THIS IS RUTH.

27:42.290 --> 27:43.928
I'M VERY SORRY TO BOTHER
YOU IN WAIKIKI,

27:44.030 --> 27:45.884
