THE KEEPER OF IT.

29:42.210 --> 29:42.733
OH.

29:42.840 --> 29:44.000
YEAH ?

29:44.110 --> 29:44.974
OKAY.

29:45.080 --> 29:46.775
NICE.

29:55.220 --> 29:55.811
WHAT ?

29:55.920 --> 29:57.751
I JUST WANT
TO LOOK.

29:57.860 --> 29:59.157
WHATEVER,

29:59.260 --> 30:00.955
