MY FAULT.

30:47.370 --> 30:50.476
ALL MY FAULT.

30:52.610 --> 30:58.219
WHAT I GAVE SOPHIA,
THE TIME AND THE ATTENTION--

30:58.320 --> 30:59.912
MONEY.

