IS GOOD FOR ME NOW.

32:19.900 --> 32:22.095
AND I THINK THAT MAYBE
IT'S GOOD FOR YOU, TOO.

32:23.470 --> 32:25.006
NO.

32:25.110 --> 32:28.307
NO, NO, IT IS
DEFINITELY NOT GOOD.

32:29.810 --> 32:31.505
DON'T YOU LOVE
ME ANYMORE ?

32:31.610 --> 32:33.271
