THROUGH DETOX ?

34:09.810 --> 34:11.698
IT'S LIKE DYING.

34:11.810 --> 34:14.574
EVERY FUCKING
MINUTE YOU DIE.

34:14.680 --> 34:17.649
GOOD.

34:17.750 --> 34:20.844
DID YOU BRING
ME SOMETHING ?

34:20.950 --> 34:23.817
NO, I HATE YOU.

34:23.920 --> 34:27.026
OH, GOD
HERE WE GO.

