34:29.100 --> 34:31.159
YOU BEAT ME AND STUCK
A GUN IN MY MOUTH.

34:31.270 --> 34:35.195
WELL, YEAH, YOU DROVE ME ALL
OVER HELL WITH A DEAD CHICK

34:35.300 --> 34:37.860
FARTING IN THE BACK OF YOUR VAN,
WHAT WAS I SUPPOSED TO DO ?

34:37.970 --> 34:39.631
YOU SCARED ME
SHITLESS.

34:39.740 --> 34:42.937
NOW I WALK AROUND ALL
THE TIME FEELING LIKE

34:43.040 --> 34:44.109
EVERYBODY'S GONNA
HUMILIATE AND MURDER ME.

34:44.210 --> 34:46.269
WELL, THEY ARE.

34:46.380 --> 34:47.608
SO I DID
YOU A FAVOR.

34:47.710 --> 34:50.417
NOW YOU'LL BE A LITTLE
MORE CAREFUL, WON'T YOU ?

34:50.520 --> 34:53.648
STOP YOUR FUCKING GAMES
FOR ONCE, YOU GODDAMN--

34:53.750 --> 34:55.251
IT'S YOUR GAME.

34:55.360 --> 34:56.349
YOU COME HERE AND YOU VISIT ME
AND YOU DON'T BRING ANYTHING,

34:56.460 --> 34:57.859
YOU JUST WANT
TO SHIT ON ME

34:57.960 --> 35:00.679
AND BREAK ME DOWN,
LIKE EVERYBODY ELSE.

35:00.790 --> 35:01.654
WELL, I WON'T
LET YOU.

35:01.760 --> 35:02.897
APOLOGIZE TO ME.

35:03.000 --> 35:04.467
FOR DEFENDING MYSELF ?

35:04.570 --> 35:06.128
FUCK YOU.

35:09.800 --> 35:11.506
YOU HAVE A FAMILY,
RIGHT ?

35:13.210 --> 35:15.906
YOU HAVE PEOPLE
LOOKING OUT FOR YOU ?

35:16.010 --> 35:18.376
YEAH, BUT--

35:18.480 --> 35:20.607
ALL I HAVE IS YOU,
DAVID, AND YOU HATE ME.

35:20.710 --> 35:23.713
YOU MADE A SPECIAL TRIP UP HERE
TO TELL ME THAT YOU HATE ME.

35:23.820 --> 35:27.745
I THINK I'M THE ONE THAT
DESERVES A GODDAMN APOLOGY.

35:32.990 --> 35:35.720
YOU REALLY ARE SICK.

35:35.830 --> 35:38.697
I'M NOT THE ONE WHO SITS IN
JAIL WHEN HE DOESN'T HAVE TO.

35:41.970 --> 35:43.858
WELL, AT LEAST YOU
KNOW HOW I FEEL.

35:43.970 --> 35:46.302
AND YOU KNOW
HOW I FEEL.

35:54.320 --> 35:57.312
LOOK, YOU CAN COME VISIT ME
AGAIN IF YOU WANT TO.

36:00.090 --> 36:02.058
NO, I WON'T BE BACK.

36:02.160 --> 36:03.616
OH.

36:04.230 --> 36:05.686
OKAY.

36:05.790 --> 36:07.428
WELL, MAYBE WHEN I GET
PAROLED YOU CAN COME

36:07.530 --> 36:09.521
AND TAKE ME
OUT TO LUNCH.

36:11.200 --> 36:12.929
PROBABLY NOT,
I'M PRETTY BUSY.

36:22.580 --> 36:24.309
I DON'T THINK YOU
CAN BE AN ARTIST

36:24.410 --> 36:26.549
WITHOUT EXPERIENCING
MAJOR SUFFERING.

36:26.650 --> 36:29.244
AND YOU HAVE TO BE SUPER-AWARE
OF THE SUFFERING AROUND YOU.

36:29.350 --> 36:33.286
AND YEAH, I'VE BEEN
INFLUENCED BY DADA AND CUBISM,

36:33.390 --> 36:35.654
BUT I ALSO FEEL LIKE
I'VE ADDED DETACHMENT

36:35.760 --> 36:38.479
AND TENDERNESS,
FOR THE NEW MILLENNIUM.

36:45.900 --> 36:48.095
THIS IS FUCKING FANTASTIC,
EVERYBODY LOVES MY SHIT.

36:48.200 --> 36:50.361
THERE'S SOMEBODY
IN HERE !

36:50.470 --> 36:51.698
HAVE YOU
TALKED TO JIMMY ?

36:51.810 --> 36:54.108
NO, EVERY TIME I SEE HIM,
SOMEBODY GRABS ME

36:54.210 --> 36:55.336
AND WANTS TO TALK
ABOUT THE PICTURES.

36:55.440 --> 36:56.805
YOU SHOULD AT LEAST
GET HIM HIGH.

36:56.910 --> 36:58.138
HERE, YOU DO IT.

36:58.250 --> 36:59.569
HOW DO YOU THINK
IT'S GOING ?

36:59.680 --> 37:01.170
WHAT ?

37:01.280 --> 37:02.110
MY SHOW, WHORE.

37:02.220 --> 37:03.118
OH.

37:03.220 --> 37:04.175
FINE, WHORE.

37:04.290 --> 37:05.541
WELL, WHAT ARE
PEOPLE SAYING ?

37:05.650 --> 37:08.016
I DON'T KNOW, I'M JUST
HANGING OUT WITH MY FRIENDS.

37:08.120 --> 37:10.281
COME ON, I WANNA KNOW
WHAT THEY'RE SAYING.

37:10.390 --> 37:13.450
DON'T DO IT ALL,
SAVE SOME FOR ME.

37:31.850 --> 37:35.172
EVERYONE IS VERY IMPRESSED
WITH CLAIRE'S PICTURES.

37:35.280 --> 37:37.043
YOU MUST BE
VERY PROUD.

37:37.150 --> 37:38.310
I CERTAINLY AM.

37:38.420 --> 37:40.741
I'M PROUD OF ALL
MY CHILDREN.

37:42.460 --> 37:44.212
NATE AND I BACK
TOGETHER AGAIN.

37:44.330 --> 37:46.958
THAT MUST SEEM
VERY SUDDEN.

37:47.060 --> 37:50.496
I MARRIED MY HUSBAND
ALMOST RIGHT AFTER WE MET.

37:50.600 --> 37:53.967
SUDDEN IS SOMETHING
I UNDERSTAND NOW.

37:54.070 --> 37:57.437
IT'S NOT
ALWAYS BEST.

37:57.540 --> 37:59.428
BUT, SOMETIMES IT IS.

38:02.580 --> 38:06.243
BRENDA, I'M GLAD NATE
IS WITH SOMEONE

38:06.350 --> 38:09.740
AND I HOPE THE THREE
OF YOU ARE VERY HAPPY.

38:12.150 --> 38:13.219
THANK YOU.

38:13.320 --> 38:16.380
HE SAYS, YOU'RE
STUDYING PSYCHOLOGY.

38:16.490 --> 38:19.653
YES, I AM GOING TO BE
A COGNITIVE THERAPIST.

38:20.960 --> 38:24.157
WHAT DOES IT MEAN WHEN
A PERSON STARTS TALKING

38:24.260 --> 38:25.818
TO HIMSELF
OUT OF NOWHERE ?

38:37.740 --> 38:39.173
NONE OF YOUR
PIECES HAVE NAMES.

38:39.280 --> 38:42.078
HOW COME ?

38:42.180 --> 38:44.842
I COULDN'T
THINK OF ANY.

38:44.950 --> 38:47.646
COME ON, DON'T BULLSHIT ME,
I'M ACTUALLY INTERESTED.

38:50.120 --> 38:55.490
WELL, I FEEL LIKE WHEN
YOU GIVE SOMETHING A NAME,

38:55.600 --> 38:57.295
PEOPLE TAKE
YOUR WORD FOR IT.

38:57.400 --> 38:59.322
WHICH IS OKAY
FOR SOME THINGS,

38:59.430 --> 39:01.432
BUT NOT THESE.

39:01.540 --> 39:04.338
I DIDN'T WANT TO TELL
ANYBODY WHAT TO SEE.

39:05.740 --> 39:08.504
IT'S LIKE MUSIC
THAT'S CALLED OPUS 15

39:08.610 --> 39:10.339
OR THREE-PART INVENTION
IN "A MINOR".

39:10.440 --> 39:12.169
WHAT'S THAT ABOUT ?

39:18.120 --> 39:20.008
YOU KNOW,
IT'S LIKE LIFE.

39:21.390 --> 39:23.779
IT'S KINDA SCARY.

39:25.490 --> 39:26.559
NO GUIDE.

39:26.660 --> 39:27.922
DON'T KNOW WHERE
I'LL END UP.

39:31.100 --> 39:32.590
YOU KNOW WHAT ?

39:35.500 --> 39:38.037
I HAVE NO FUCKING IDEA
WHAT THESE PICTURES MEAN.

39:40.170 --> 39:41.239
I KNOW.

39:41.340 --> 39:43.399
ISN'T IT GREAT ?

39:48.880 --> 39:49.847
ROGER, YOU DON'T
NEED A BODYGUARD.

39:49.950 --> 39:51.144
YES, I DO.

39:51.250 --> 39:53.639
LOOK, I HAVE ENEMIES.

39:53.750 --> 39:56.287
THERE ARE FUCKERS OUT THERE THAT
WOULD DO ANYTHING TO GET ME.

39:56.390 --> 39:58.085
ANYTHING.

39:58.190 --> 40:00.658
I JUST WANT
TO FEEL SAFE.

40:00.760 --> 40:04.628
AND I WILL PAY YOU
A SHITLOAD OF MONEY.

40:09.400 --> 40:10.731
WELL, I COULDN'T WORK
FOR YOU EXCLUSIVELY,

40:10.840 --> 40:13.365
IT WOULD HAVE TO BE A FREELANCE,
WHEN-I-CAN SITUATION.

40:13.470 --> 40:15.631
I'M SURE WE CAN FIGURE
SOMETHING OUT.

40:15.740 --> 40:17.378
WE'LL DRAW UP
A CONTRACT.

40:17.480 --> 40:19.641
FIRST, I NEED SOMETHING
IN WRITING THAT SAYS

40:19.750 --> 40:20.842
YOU'RE GOING TO DROP
OUR LAWSUIT.

40:20.950 --> 40:21.939
FOREVER.

40:22.050 --> 40:24.610
OH, ALRIGHT.

40:30.020 --> 40:31.658
IS THAT ONE OF THE PEOPLE
YOU'RE AFRAID OF ?

40:31.760 --> 40:33.887
NO.

40:33.990 --> 40:35.696
THAT'S STEVE.

40:35.800 --> 40:38.928
HE STAYS IN THE GUEST
HOUSE SOMETIMES.

40:45.310 --> 40:46.402
WELL ?

40:46.510 --> 40:50.071
I'LL GIVE IT SERIOUS
CONSIDERATION.

41:02.860 --> 41:04.316
I WASN'T SURE
YOU'D BE HERE.

41:04.420 --> 41:06.354
OF COURSE
I'M HERE.

41:06.460 --> 41:08.724
YOU WERE MY STUDENT,
MY ASSISTANT,

41:08.830 --> 41:10.024
YOU THINK THAT MEANS
NOTHING TO ME ?

41:10.130 --> 41:13.588
IT'S MY RESPONSIBILITY
AND MY PLEASURE

41:13.700 --> 41:15.133
TO SUPPORT YOU, CLAIRE.

41:15.240 --> 41:16.264
WOW.

41:16.370 --> 41:17.928
BESIDES,
YOU'RE COMPETITION, NOW.

41:18.040 --> 41:20.964
THOUGH I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE
RUSSELL FIRST IN THIS POSITION.

41:21.070 --> 41:22.901
WELL, YOU
WERE WRONG.

41:23.010 --> 41:23.977
BECAUSE IT'S ME.

41:26.180 --> 41:28.478
AND SO IT
ALL BEGINS.

41:28.580 --> 41:32.209
WITH THE FIRST SUCCESS,
CORRUPTION.

41:32.320 --> 41:35.289
IT'S CORRUPT TO FEEL LIKE
I FINALLY DID SOMETHING RIGHT ?

41:35.390 --> 41:36.982
ACTUALLY,
YES, IT IS.

41:37.090 --> 41:38.978
YOU'LL SEE.

41:39.090 --> 41:41.854
BUT SO WHAT ?

41:41.960 --> 41:43.222
WHO WANTS TO BE
A SAINT, RIGHT ?

41:43.330 --> 41:45.218
NOT ME.

41:45.330 --> 41:46.365
NO, NO ONE DOES

41:46.470 --> 41:49.496
AND THE WORK SUFFERS.

41:51.100 --> 41:53.568
I TOAST YOU WITH
THIS SHITTY WINE.

42:00.980 --> 42:01.742
HELLO THERE.

42:01.850 --> 42:04.341
WELL, YOU LOOK
RECOVERED.

42:04.450 --> 42:07.214
I FEEL FABULOUS.

42:07.320 --> 42:09.185
EVERYONE SHOULD
DROP AN ORGAN,

42:09.290 --> 42:10.757
AFTER THE FIRST SHOCK,

42:10.860 --> 42:12.828
IT'S POSITIVELY
LIBERATING.

42:14.960 --> 42:16.598
SO, IS THIS THE FRUIT
OF NATE'S LOINS ?

42:16.700 --> 42:20.864
MAYA,
THIS IS MARGARET.

42:23.200 --> 42:24.633
LOOK.

42:24.740 --> 42:25.764
DON'T TAKE THIS PERSONALLY,
BUT I DON'T THINK SHE LIKES YOU.

42:25.870 --> 42:26.939
SHE HARDLY KNOWS
YOU'RE HERE.

42:27.040 --> 42:30.430
MARGARET CAN'T HELP
TRYING TO MAKE US

42:30.540 --> 42:31.973
FEEL BAD
ABOUT OURSELVES.

42:32.080 --> 42:34.401
YOU KNOW, BRENDA,

42:34.510 --> 42:36.478
IT'S UNETHICAL TO USE
AN INNOCENT CHILD

42:36.580 --> 42:38.138
TO EXPRESS
YOUR RESENTMENT.

42:42.090 --> 42:43.159
CLAIRE.

42:43.260 --> 42:44.784
DO YOU DO
COMMISSIONS ?

42:44.890 --> 42:46.721
UH, YES.

42:46.830 --> 42:48.991
WELL, I WANT YOU
TO PHOTOGRAPH OLIVIER AND ME

42:49.100 --> 42:52.194
AND DO THAT THING YOU DO, ONLY
MIX ALL OUR PIECES TOGETHER.

42:52.300 --> 42:55.895
THAT WILL BE
A PORTRAIT.

42:58.100 --> 43:01.069
KUDOS, DARLING,
YOU'RE BRILLIANT.

43:07.680 --> 43:08.499
CONGRATULATIONS.

43:08.620 --> 43:11.339
THANK YOU.

43:14.550 --> 43:16.051
EXCUSE ME.

43:25.270 --> 43:26.294
HEY.

43:26.400 --> 43:28.368
CONGRATULATIONS.

43:28.470 --> 43:29.789
THANK YOU,

43:29.900 --> 43:30.832
LOOK, THERE'S SOMEBODY
WHO MAY WANT TO BUY SOMETHING,

43:30.940 --> 43:31.565
I'LL BE BACK
IN ONE MINUTE.

43:31.670 --> 43:33.399
WHAT THE FUCK ?

43:33.510 --> 43:34.408
ARE YOU
BLOWING ME OFF ?

43:34.510 --> 43:35.977
NO.

43:36.080 --> 43:37.479
YOU HAVEN'T SAID SHIT
TO ME SINCE I GOT HERE,

43:37.580 --> 43:39.639
I MEAN,
WHAT THE FUCK ?

43:39.750 --> 43:41.240
I THINK IT'S PRETTY
FUCKING RUDE.

43:41.350 --> 43:42.840
OKAY.

43:42.950 --> 43:45.009
MAYBE YOU DIDN'T
REALIZE THIS,

43:45.120 --> 43:46.781
BUT I'M A LITTLE
FUCKING BUSY RIGHT NOW,

43:46.890 --> 43:47.879
I'M IN THE MIDDLE
OF MY FUCKING SHOW.

43:47.990 --> 43:49.810
MAYBE YOU
DON'T REMEMBER,

43:49.920 --> 43:53.083
BUT I'M THE ONE WHO FUCKING
GOT YOU THIS FUCKING SHOW.

43:55.400 --> 43:56.822
JIMMY.

44:00.800 --> 44:03.394
WELL, FUCK YOU, THEN.

44:03.500 --> 44:05.639
FUCK YOU ALL.

44:36.270 --> 44:37.396
HI, MICHAELA.

44:37.500 --> 44:38.933
HI, UNCLE NATE.

44:43.010 --> 44:44.136
I GAVE THE BOOK
TO DAVID.

44:44.240 --> 44:45.673
THANK YOU.

44:45.780 --> 44:48.169
HE LIKED IT A LOT.

44:54.690 --> 44:56.112
THERE WAS
A PICTURE IN IT.

44:56.220 --> 44:57.812
I KNOW.

44:57.920 --> 45:00.059
WHERE'D THE PICTURE
COME FROM ?

45:03.660 --> 45:05.389
DO YOU KNOW
WHO TOOK IT ?

45:09.040 --> 45:10.439
WHY'D YOU PUT
IT IN THE BOOK ?

45:10.540 --> 45:13.839
YOU SHOULD TALK
TO MY DAD.

45:13.940 --> 45:15.407
HE'S IN THE OFFICE.

45:32.790 --> 45:35.122
GOD, YOU FREAK, WHEN
ARE YOU GONNA LET IT GO ?

45:35.230 --> 45:38.495
WHEN YOU ADMIT, IN PUBLIC,
THAT I AM PART OF YOUR WORK.

45:38.600 --> 45:40.989
YOU'RE NOT !

45:41.100 --> 45:43.660
I CREATED THESE PIECES, THEY
ARE MINE AND PEOPLE LOVE THEM.

45:43.770 --> 45:45.658
I LOVE YOU.

45:45.770 --> 45:47.601
YOU LOVE ?

45:47.710 --> 45:48.904
YOU FUCKED A MAN
AND LIED ABOUT IT.

45:49.010 --> 45:50.329
YOU FUCKED A WOMAN !

45:50.440 --> 45:51.702
NOT WHEN I WAS
WITH YOU !

45:51.810 --> 45:54.404
NO, YOU JUST WENT AND HAD
AN ABORTION WITHOUT ME !

45:54.510 --> 45:57.775
DON'T YOU
DARE GO THERE.

45:57.880 --> 45:59.017
DON'T YOU
FUCKING DARE !

45:59.120 --> 46:00.542
IS THERE
A PROBLEM, GUYS ?

46:00.650 --> 46:04.484
YOU ARE SO
DEEPLY IRRELEVANT.

46:08.800 --> 46:10.199
ARE YOU FUCKING
HIM NOW ?

46:12.100 --> 46:13.692
YOU FUCKED JIMMY
TO GET A GALLERY,

46:13.800 --> 46:16.997
WHAT CAN BILLY CHENOWITH
DO FOR YOU ?

46:17.100 --> 46:18.567
YOU ASSHOLE,
I FUCKING HATE YOU.

46:18.670 --> 46:19.762
THIS HAS
TO STOP NOW.

46:19.870 --> 46:21.098
IT'S TIME
TO LEAVE.

46:21.210 --> 46:22.507
JUST LEAVE.

46:22.610 --> 46:24.498
THIS NEEDS TO STOP.

46:24.610 --> 46:26.475
OUT.

46:38.930 --> 46:40.420
ARE YOU ALRIGHT ?

46:43.460 --> 46:45.064
TAKE ME HOME.

46:54.810 --> 46:56.368
ARE YOU CRAZY ?

46:56.480 --> 46:58.675
IF I WAS YOU, FELLA,
I'D MOVE ON DOWN THE ROAD

46:58.780 --> 47:00.179
BEFORE BARB FINDS
OUT YOU'RE HERE.

47:00.280 --> 47:01.747
HOYT, I'LL ASK YOU
ONE MORE TIME

47:01.850 --> 47:03.340
AND THEN I'M
CALLING THE POLICE.

47:03.450 --> 47:04.986
WHOA, WHOA.

47:05.090 --> 47:06.614
DID YOU TAKE
THAT PICTURE ?

47:06.720 --> 47:09.780
SHE'S A KIMMEL,

47:09.890 --> 47:13.018
WE TEND TO POINT
CAMERAS AT EACH OTHER.

47:13.130 --> 47:17.453
SOMEBODY OBVIOUSLY TOOK IT,
MAYBE IT WAS ME.

47:17.560 --> 47:20.290
NO, I REMEMBER THIS,
THIS WAS A COUPLE OF YEARS AGO.

47:20.400 --> 47:22.265
WE HAD A PICNIC.

47:24.470 --> 47:26.006
YOU'RE A FUCKING LIAR.

47:27.840 --> 47:29.307
YOU WERE WITH THERE WITH LISA
ON THE BEACH THE DAY SHE DIED.

47:29.410 --> 47:30.399
NO.

47:30.510 --> 47:31.977
YES, YOU WERE.

47:32.080 --> 47:34.503
AND THIS PROVES IT.

47:37.720 --> 47:39.039
YOU SONOFABITCH,
WHAT DID YOU DO TO HER ?

47:39.150 --> 47:42.051
NOTHING, GOD, NOTHING !

47:44.420 --> 47:47.355
THIS WAS A PLACE
THAT WE USED TO GO.

47:47.460 --> 47:49.621
I'D DRIVE SOUTH
AND I'D MEET HER THERE.

47:49.730 --> 47:51.357
ALONE ?

47:51.460 --> 47:53.599
MAYBE, A FEW TIMES.

47:53.700 --> 47:55.031
YEAH.

47:55.900 --> 47:57.538
WHY ?

48:04.380 --> 48:06.473
WE HAD A THING.

48:06.580 --> 48:08.047
IT WAS ON AND OFF...

48:09.450 --> 48:10.815
BUT IT WAS INTENSE.

48:10.920 --> 48:12.285
YOU KNOW LISA...

48:13.390 --> 48:15.210
SHE WAS INTENSE.

48:17.890 --> 48:19.448
WHEN WAS THIS ?

48:20.530 --> 48:21.588
WHEN WE
WERE MARRIED ?

48:21.690 --> 48:23.021
BEFORE.

48:25.770 --> 48:27.419
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

48:30.170 --> 48:32.661
SHE TOLD ME WHAT IT
WAS LIKE TO BE YOUR WIFE.

48:34.810 --> 48:36.004
WHAT THE FUCK
IS WRONG WITH YOU ?

48:36.110 --> 48:37.668
WHY DID YOU PUT HER
THROUGH ALL THAT ?

48:37.780 --> 48:39.145
1--

48:39.250 --> 48:41.571
YOU THINK SHE JUST SPENT HER
WHOLE LIFE WAITING FOR YOU ?

48:42.580 --> 48:44.275
PEOPLE LOVED LISA.

48:46.120 --> 48:48.418
AND SHE LOVED US BACK.

48:50.190 --> 48:52.249
YOU KNOW, SHE MIGHT HAVE
KILLED HERSELF BECAUSE OF YOU.

48:52.360 --> 48:55.227
OH YEAH, DID YOU EVER
THINK ABOUT THAT ?

49:00.230 --> 49:02.266
LISTEN, LET'S TAKE
A WALK, OKAY ?

49:02.370 --> 49:03.689
THIS IS A BIG
MISUNDERSTANDING.

49:03.800 --> 49:04.869
NO, NO, NO !

49:04.970 --> 49:06.699
LISA WOULD NEVER
KILL HERSELF !

49:07.670 --> 49:09.103
I KNOW THAT.

49:09.210 --> 49:11.974
SHE MIGHT LEAVE ME,
BUT SHE WOULD NEVER LEAVE MAYA.

49:14.680 --> 49:18.116
SO YOU TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED
ON THAT BEACH RIGHT NOW.

49:18.220 --> 49:20.040
RIGHT THE FUCK NOW !

49:29.100 --> 49:31.751
I WANTED SOME TIME
BY OURSELVES.

49:31.860 --> 49:33.669
LISA SAID SHE
WASN'T INTO IT.

49:33.770 --> 49:35.988
YOU KNOW, CLEAN SLATE,
NEVER AGAIN.

49:36.100 --> 49:38.091
OKAY, FINE.

49:40.270 --> 49:42.135
I COULDN'T LET
HER TELL BARB.

49:49.050 --> 49:51.939
I DID NOT GET
ANGRY WITH HER.

49:52.050 --> 49:54.314
I PLAYED THE GUITAR,
I SANG HER A SONG.

49:55.690 --> 49:57.089
I SANG HER A SONG...

49:59.690 --> 50:01.089
AND WE...

50:05.600 --> 50:07.158
WENT OUR
SEPARATE WAYS.

50:08.900 --> 50:10.492
(crying )

50:20.380 --> 50:20.903
( gunshot)

50:21.010 --> 50:22.511
AAHH !

52:06.150 --> 52:10.519
( police radio chatter)

52:59.770 --> 53:01.533
GEORGE ?

53:11.980 --> 53:13.538
GEORGE ?

53:17.620 --> 53:19.850
HAVE YOU BEEN HERE
ALL NIGHT ?

53:19.960 --> 53:23.157
I HAD TO PUT THINGS IN ORDER
AND I GUESS I FELL ASLEEP.

53:23.260 --> 53:25.694
DIDN'T MEAN
TO WORRY YOU.

53:26.330 --> 53:27.866
NO HARM DONE.

53:29.130 --> 53:31.997
COME ON, LET'S GO
BACK TO THE HOUSE.

53:32.100 --> 53:33.738
I CAN'T DO THAT.

53:33.840 --> 53:37.936
YES, YOU CAN, DEAR,
IT'S WHERE WE LIVE.

53:38.040 --> 53:40.440
NO, RUTH.

53:40.550 --> 53:44.418
THIS IS WHERE
I LIVE NOW.

55:05.130 --> 55:06.961
LET'S GET MARRIED
AND HAVE A BABY.

55:08.770 --> 55:09.930
WILL YOU ?

55:10.040 --> 55:11.962
YES.

55:19.240 --> 55:22.038
(thunder)

55:59.990 --> 56:01.218
OH, GOOD.

56:01.320 --> 56:02.719
MY BOUGAINVILLEA
NEEDS THIS.

56:04.690 --> 56:06.453
YOU WERE BRAVE
TO FACE HIM.

56:08.790 --> 56:09.825
NOT REALLY.

56:09.930 --> 56:10.828
THERE WAS A GUARD.

56:10.930 --> 56:11.828
DOESN'T MATTER.

